[[哈利波特系列電影|哈利波特系列電影]]裡，由[[陶比·瓊斯|陶比·瓊斯]]為多比一角[[配音|配音]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0001024/|title=Dobby (Character)|accessdate=2018-05-11|publisher=IMDB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407090405/http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0001024/|archivedate=2017-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/harry-potter-countdown-toby-jones-say-unrepeatable-franchise-will-stand-alone-forever/|title=‘Harry Potter’ countdown: Toby Jones say ‘unrepeatable’ franchise will stand alone forever|date=2010-10-15|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2018-05-12|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150916235646/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/harry-potter-countdown-toby-jones-say-unrepeatable-franchise-will-stand-alone-forever/|archivedate=2015-09-16}}</ref>。

《[[哈利波特：火盃的考驗_(電影)|火盃的考驗]]》和《[[哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令_(電影)|鳳凰會的密令]]》兩部電影中，恰好多比於原著小說裡的所作所為都被一律改由[[奈威·隆巴顿|奈威·隆巴頓]]來完成<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-harry-potter-characters/|title=The 25 Greatest Harry Potter Characters|accessdate=2018-06-30|date=2011-07-26|work=Empire|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801122239/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/greatest-harry-potter-characters/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==評價==
在[[IGN|IGN]]的「前25名哈利波特人物」中多比名列第24位，他的死亡被視為該系列中「最令人感動的時刻之一」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/26/top-25-harry-potter-characters|title=Top 25 Harry Potter Characters|accessdate=2018-05-11|date=2017-06-26|last=Staff|first=I. G. N.|work=IGN|language=en-US|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108173001/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/26/top-25-harry-potter-characters|archivedate=2017-11-08}}</ref>。在NextMovie.com網站做的哈利波特電影[[民意調查|民意調查]]中，多比獲選為最受歡迎的[[哈利波特中的生物|魔法生物]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2806194/harry-potter-poll-results/|title='Harry Potter' Mega Poll: The Mega Results! - MTV|accessdate=2018-05-11|date=2017-06-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608223159/http://www.mtv.com/news/2806194/harry-potter-poll-results/|archivedate=2017-06-08}}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》選出的25名最偉大的《哈利波特》人物中，多比名列第九位<ref name=":2" />。

2015年媒體報導，一些參觀[[倫敦|倫敦]][[华纳兄弟利维斯登工作室|華納兄弟工作室]]之旅的哈利波特書迷會將襪子留在多比的雕像旁，以象徵似地讓多比「獲得自由」<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/harry-potter-fans-are-trying-to-free-dobby-by-leaving-socks-on-the-warner-bros-studio-tour-a6674936.html|title=Harry Potter fans are trying to free Dobby by leaving socks on the Warner Bros Studio Tour|author=Jess Denham|date=2015-10-01|work=The Independent|accessdate=2018-10-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010101128/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/harry-potter-fans-are-trying-to-free-dobby-by-leaving-socks-on-the-warner-bros-studio-tour-a6674936.html|archivedate=2015-10-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/harry-potter-fans-determined-free-6572195|title=Harry Potter fans have a pretty clever way of freeing Dobby from this museum|last=Shammas|first=John|date=2015-10-04|newspaper=mirror|accessdate=2018-10-12|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129110623/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/harry-potter-fans-determined-free-6572195|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

